IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SELL.

DATA DIVISION.

WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 SELL-QTY     PIC 9(5).
01 SELL-QTY-STR PIC X(5).
01 TOTAL-COST PIC 9(8).

LINKAGE SECTION.
01 LK-MONEY PIC 9(6).
01 LK-INGOT-STOCK PIC 9(5).
01 LK-INGOT-PRICE PIC 9(4).

PROCEDURE DIVISION USING LK-MONEY LK-INGOT-STOCK LK-INGOT-PRICE.
  MOVE 0 TO SELL-QTY
  MOVE SPACES TO SELL-QTY-STR

  PERFORM UNTIL SELL-QTY > 0
    DISPLAY "いくつ売却しますか？(現在価格：" LK-INGOT-PRICE "G)"
    DISPLAY "所持インゴット：" LK-INGOT-STOCK "個"
    DISPLAY "キャンセルする場合は0を入力してください"
    ACCEPT SELL-QTY-STR

    IF FUNCTION TRIM(SELL-QTY-STR) IS NOT NUMERIC
      DISPLAY "数字を入力してください"
      MOVE 0 TO SELL-QTY
    ELSE
      MOVE FUNCTION TRIM(SELL-QTY-STR) TO SELL-QTY

      IF SELL-QTY = 0
        DISPLAY "キャンセルしました"
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
      END-IF
    END-IF
  END-PERFORM

  COMPUTE TOTAL-COST = SELL-QTY * LK-INGOT-PRICE

  IF LK-INGOT-STOCK >= SELL-QTY
    COMPUTE LK-MONEY = LK-MONEY + TOTAL-COST
    SUBTRACT SELL-QTY FROM LK-INGOT-STOCK
    DISPLAY SELL-QTY "個売却しました！（+" TOTAL-COST "G）"
    DISPLAY "所持金：" LK-MONEY "G"
    DISPLAY "所持インゴット：" LK-INGOT-STOCK "個"
  ELSE
    DISPLAY "インゴットが足りません"
  END-IF

  GOBACK.
